'''Handelmort Mansion''' is a mansion found in [[East Ardougne]], just west of [[Ardougne market]]. It plays a large role in the [[Tribal Totem]] [[quest]]. Home to [[Lord Francis Kurt Handelmort]], a wealthy East Ardougne noble, the mansion is richly decorated. It is also home to some artefacts that Lord Handelmort has taken. He has gone to great lengths to protect these artefacts with [[guard dog]]s, locked house, and a booby-trapped staircase.

